Class DaoFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.horsego.dao.DaoFactory

  • public class DaoFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Class factory for getting instances of classes that implement the Dao interface. A static method getInstance() is used to get an instance of this class.

    1.0
